name: The Arya Sweater
description:
ARYA FANTASTIC.

Inspired by actress Maisie Williams as the young Stark wolf with sass in Game of Thrones. Arya Stark will always be the coolest kid on the block in any universe.

Made of pure organic cotton. Fair trade certified. Ladies' fit. 

Ethically produced in India. Digitally printed in Europe.

name: The Dwarven Sweater
description:
Good things come in thirteens! 

Stave off the cold weather with Thorin Oakenshield and company. With thirteen dwarves to keep you cosy, (name them all! Thorin, Nori, Dori, Ori, Bifur, Bofur, Bombur, Oin, Gloin, Dwalin, Balin, Fili and Kili) it will be a very merry Christmas indeed in your Hobbit-hole. 

Made of pure organic cotton. Fair trade certified. 

Ethically produced in India. Digitally printed in Europe.

name: The Legolas Sweater
description: Because YOU ONLY LEGOLAS ONCE. Pair the Legolas jumper with our Thranduil tee-shirt to experience the Mirkwood-ian magic that is the grumpy Elvenking father and his sea-longing, Gimli-loving son. Inspired by the princolas of Mirkwood, Legolas Greenleaf, as portrayed by Orlando Bloom in Peter Jackson's Lord of the Rings and Hobbit movies. Made of pure organic cotton. Fair trade certified. Ladies' fit. Ethically produced in India. Digitally printed in Europe.

name: The Danse Unisex Sweater
description:
DANSE ON TIL DAWN.

Until your toes bleed, until your body aches. Because it's all you know, and it's what you love.

This grey unisex sweater features a crew neck collar and raglan sleeves, and is super fleecy and snuggly.

Digitally printed. Made of pure organic fair-trade cotton. Ethically produced in India.

name: The Markova Sweater
description:
I GOT THE MOVES LIKE MARKOVA. 

This statement-making raglan sweater has a pretty floral motif and can be layered over leotards and tops during winter and worn on it's own during the less frigid fall and spring months.

Made of pure, fair-trade organic cotton. Ladies' fit.

Ethically produced in India. Digitally printed in Europe.

name: The Vishneva Sweater
description:
Inspired by the amaaaazing Diana Vishneva's Giselle, this super-soft sweater is the perfect thing to keep you warm in the studio or on the street.

Made of pure, fair-trade organic cotton. Ladies' fit.

Ethically produced in India. Digitally printed in Europe.

name: The Floral Lung Unisex Sweater
description:
Just breathe.

Featuring out fall floral motif. Unisex fit with a crewneck collar.

Digitally printed. Made of pure, fair-trade organic cotton. Ethically produced in India.

name: The Baryshnikov Unisex/Manshirt
description: BOOGIE LIKE BARYSHNIKOV. Introducing our first-ever manshirt! The ladies may get to prance around in their fancy leotards and skirts, but you get to rock up to class channeling Mikhail Baryshnikov and out-sass them all. And if you're a lady, you can wear this and your fancy leotard - it's called having your cake and eating it. Boom! Made of soft and fine Turkish cotton. Digitally-printed. Slim-fit.

name: The Fouetté Unisex/Manshirt
description:
May the Fouetté be with you.

Our bestselling Fouetté shirt, now available for the wearing pleasure of ballet boys (and men). 

Made of soft and fine Turkish cotton. Digitally-printed. Slim-fit.

name: The Fouetté Oversized Boyfriend Shirt
description: "Use the Fouetté, Luke!" "Luke, I AM YOUR FOUETTÉ." As featured by Pointe magazine! This boyfriend tunic shirt features our fall floral motif, along with some sage advice to ballet dancers. It has an oversized, boxy fit, a wide collar and softly-rolled sleeves, and is the perfect piece of clothing to throwover your leotard in between classes. Made of beautifully fine, pure, Turkish cotton.

name: The Jeté Tank
description:
Jeté  en l'air like you don't care! For dancers who don't just tour.

This tank is cut for a loose fit for ethereal lightness and drape, with a curved back hem, making it wonderfully versatile whether layered over ballet leotards or worn on its on with a pair of jeans.

Made of natural and luxuriously silken Tencel.

name: The Stardust Tank
description:
WE ARE ALL STARSDUST. A shirt inspired by Svetlana Zakharova's Odette in Swan Lake. 

Melange-grey tank with a curved back hem, cut in a loose fit with that drapes and flows wonderfully when worn. Perfect on its on or thrown over a leotard during rehearsal.

Made of natural and luxuriously silken Tencel.

name: The Oversplit Tank
description:
A cascade of florals surrounding a gymnast in training, emblazoned on a soft white tank.

This tank is cut for a loose fit for ethereal lightness and drape, with a curved back hem, making it wonderfully versatile whether layered over leotards or worn on its on with a pair of jeans.

Made of natural and luxuriously silken Tencel.

name: The Turnout Cropped Shirt
description:
The dancer's mantra: turn up and turn out.

This cropped shirt has a wide collar that can be worn for an off-shoulder style and a loose, boxy fit that makes it an ideal layering piece.

Made of luxuriously silky, natural Tencel.

name: Lace Ballet Wrap Skirt - Seafoam
description:
This diaphonous wrap skirt is tailored from a romantic seafoam-hued lace with a subtle shimmer. It is finished with a robin's blue silk satin ribbon and a fine rolled hem. 

Perfect whether worn in everyday rehearsals or for that extra-special audition. 

This skirt will be custom-made for you when you order. It is 12" long and is available in 3 sizes.

Small: 24" - 26" waists
Medium: 27 - 29" waists
Large: 30 - 32" waists

name: Scalloped Lace Ballet Wrap Skirt - Peach
description: This floaty, ethereal ballet wrap skirt is made with 1.5 meters of exquisite Japanese chantilly lace in peach. This lace has a pretty floral motiff, and floaty scalloped hem. It is finished with a peach satin ribbon to wrap around the waist. Wear it on it's own during rehearsals, and slip our lilac pull-on skirt underneath after to create a stylish, street-ready skirt. This skirt will be custom-made for you when you order. It is available in 2 lengths - 11" and 14". Due to the wrap-around style, this skirt can fit most 23" to 31" waists. Please allow 2 - 3 weeks from date of ordering for your skirt to be completed.

name: Scalloped Lace Ballet Wrap Skirt - Diamond
description:
This ballet wrap skirt is a truly exquisite piece for any dancer. 

It is made with 1.5 meters of very fine, gossamer-light Japanese lace. The diamond colourway has pearl, gold and silver threads woven into a floral motif. It has a unique scalloped hem, and is finished with a ivory satin ribbon to tie around your waist.

This skirt will be custom-made for you when you order. It is available in 2 lengths -  11" and 14". 

Due to the wrap-around style, this skirt can fit waist sizes between 23" to 31".

Please allow 2 - 3 weeks from date of ordering for your skirt to be completed.

name: Scalloped Lace Ballet Wrap Skirt - Lilac
description:
Crafted from German lace with a feminine rose pattern, this ballet wrap skirt features a delicate scalloped hem, satin ribbon tie and 1.5 meters of gathered lace designed to flow subtly with a dancer's every movement.

This skirt will be custom-made for you when you order. It is available in 2 lengths -  11" and 14". 

Due to the wrap-around style, this skirt can fit 23" to 31" waists.

Please allow 2 - 3 weeks from date of ordering for your skirt to be completed.

name: Pleated Contrast Lace Skirt - Ready-to-Wear
description:
This beautifully feminine skirt is cut from seafoam lace, with contrasting trim and lining made of translucent chiffon in the softest shade of blush. 

A final lining of coral-coloured acetate adds structure and volume. This skirt has a side-zip, and a hook-and-bar clasp.

This skirt will be custom-made for you when you order, and will be tailored an awesome local seamstress trained in Shanghainese and Hong Kong techniques (we love her so). 

Please allow 2 - 3 weeks for your order to be completed.

Small: 24" - 26" waists
Medium: 27 - 29" waists
Large: 30 - 32" waists

name: Pull-On Ballet Skirt - Lilac
description:
A ballet skirt with all the elegance and ease of movement of a wrap skirt, minus the need to tie it on and adjust it to your waist.

This lilac silk-chiffon skirt simply slips on thanks to the thin elastic-waistband, yet allows for completely free movement when dancing thanks to the wrap-effect front. 

The gathered waist adds beautfilly subtle ripple and flow to the skirt.

This skirt will be custom-made for you when you order. It can fit waist sizes between 23" - 31", thanks to the stretch elastic waistband.

Please allow 2 - 3 weeks from date of ordering for your skirt to be completed.

name: The Gymnastics Legends Unisex Sweater
description:
Svetlana Khorkhina. Anna Pavlova. Nastia Liukin. Nadia Comaneci. Olga Korbut. Mo Huilan. Daniela Silivas. 

We wanted to celebrate the greats of women's gymnastics as we knew best: by fitting as many of them as we could onto this sweater. 

Made of pure organic cotton. Fair trade certified. Unisex fit.

Ethically produced in India. Digitally printed in Europe.

name: The Izbasa Poster
description:
An A3 size poster of Romanian gymnast and two-time Olympic champion, the gorgeous Sandra Izbasa. 

Digitally printed on 160 gsm glossy art paper. Poster measures 11" x 17".

name: The Maroney Poster
description:
This poster features US Olympian, she of the Amanar and not-impressed fame, McKayla Maroney.

Digitally printed on 160 gsm glossy art paper. Poster measures 10" x 16".

name: The Bessonova Poster
description:
The glorious Anna Bessonova epitomizes grace, elegance and an insane amount of discipline, and was the perfect subject for our first ever rhythmic gymnastics poster.

Digitally printed on 160 gsm glossy art paper. Poster measures 10" x 16".

name: The Moors Poster
description:
This poster features the queen of sass herself, fan-favourite Canadian gymnast Victoria Moors. 

Here's hoping that she'll get the double-double layout named for her in Antwerp!

Digitally printed on 160 gsm glossy art paper. Poster measures 10" x 16".

name: The Summer Daisies Necklace
description: This necklace is comprised of enamel daisies with crystal buds and pearl clusters, with a lobster-claw clasp at the back. Wear it with a simple white top for maximum impact, or with the Summer Daisies ring set for a fun, floral summer! Chain measures 16". Available in elegant black or sweet seafoam.

name: The Flower Cluster Ring
description:
Enamel daisies, golden sunflowers, and a lilac glass flower in bloom sit alongside butterflies and stars come together in an array of sweet summer hues. 

This is the ultimate summer pastiche ring, sure to complement any bright frock or liven up a simple outfit!

This ring comes with an adjustable gold band, and should fit standard ring sizes 5 - 9.

name: The Summer Daisies Ring Set
description:
This set comprises of two pastel-coloured summer daisy rings studded with brilliant crystals. These rings look lovely when worn on their own, or can be combined to make a statement piece.

They come with adjustable gold bands, and can fit between standard ring-sizes 5 - 9.

name: The Little Deer Ring Set
description:
A set of three stack rings featuring pink roses, a crystal, and a blush-tailed fawn.

These rings can be worn individually, or together, to create a mini woodland scene on your finger. 

These come with adjustable gold bands, and can fit between standard ring-sizes 5 - 9.

name: The Little Dove Ring Set
description:
A set of three stack rings comprising of a bird in flight, a crystal-budded flower in bloom, and a coloured-glass crystal gem.

These rings can be worn individually or together, making them perfect for bright summer days!

Rings come with adjustable gold bands, and should fit standard ring sizes 5 - 9.

Available in lilac or bluebird.

name: The Ivory Rose Ring
description:
This vintage-inspired ring is just about one of the loveliest things with seen. The ivory-hued rose set amongst coloured crystal gems emanates charm and elegance.

This ring comes with an adustable gold band that should fit standard ring sizes 5 - 9.

name: The Forget-me-not Hairpins
description: These lovely forget-me-not clusters and a sweet yet subtle way to wear flowers in your hair this spring. A trio of these pins would match perfectly with our flower cluster ring. Available in pink, lilac and bluebird.

name: The Summer Days Hairpins
description: Summer stars, purple crocuses and buttery-yellow marigolds are the perfect things to put your hair up with! Pair them with our forget-me-not hairpins for the perfect dreamy summer 'do.

name: Custom Order - Unisex/Man Shirts
description: We only offer ladyshirts in stock, but we offer custom made-to-order unisex shirts. Any design can be printed onto a unisex crewneck shirt. Your shirt will be printed especially for you, and shipped to you from our printingfolk friends in the United States. Please state your desired design in your Paypal notes, or contact us after you place your order.

name: Custom Order - XL & 2XL Shirts
description: We only offer S, M and L shirts in stock, but we offer custom XL and 2XL shirts. Any design can be printed onto either a crewneck or v-neck shirt.
